reviewText: I was very angry that I wasted my money on this awful P.O.S. This was twice as bad as the first, I actually puked in my lap before I could finish watching it.

liquid television takes animation to extremes that only MTV fans can truly appreciate. it has everything from simplistic "stick figure theatre" to some of the most talented and sofisticated animation artists around. the unavailability of season box sets is inexcusable.
